Order By Statement Ascending:

SELECT column_1, column_2 
FROM table_name
ORDER BY column_1 ASC;

Order By Statement Descending:

SELECT column_1, column_2 
FROM table_name
ORDER BY column_1 DESC;


View first and last names of customers in asceneding order of last names.

SELECT first_name, last_name FROM customer
ORDER BY last_name ASC; 

View first and last names of customers in descending order of last names

SELECT first_name, last_name FROM customer
ORDER BY last_name DESC; 

Display the customer ID of the top 10 highest payments:

SELECT customer_id FROM payment
ORDER BY amount DESC
LIMIT 10;
